            "title": "北京市稅務局原局長李亞民受查",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"北京市稅務局原局長李亞民涉違紀違法受查。中新社微信公眾號\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1f74342fe1b81a2d5f2e0b555e3a211e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032810225340433.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">北京市稅務局原局長李亞民涉違紀違法受查。中新社微信公眾號</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中央紀委國家監委網站通報，中央紀委國家監委駐國家稅務總局紀檢監察組、遼寧省紀委監委消息，國家稅務總局北京市稅務局原黨委書記、局長李亞民涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，目前正接受中央紀委國家監委駐國家稅務總局紀檢監察組紀律審查和遼寧省遼陽市監察委員會監察調查。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
